quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  23,75,"Sinndo Men Yurmino …ìe Men ittani …ìe ko he…ìi …ìe kon immorde e kokke e heege …ìe duumotono e ndr majjere ma…ì…ìe gaayi Goonga kan hara hi…ìe mema wa…óa yaha-yilto."
  23,76,"Gom…óii Men jaribiimo…ìe nooneeji masiibooji, …ìe hoykinanaaki Joomi ma…ì…ìe …ìe yankinanaaki Mo, …ìe yankinaaki …ìe noddi Mo fii yo O ittan …ìe masiibooji …óin tuma jippagol majji."
  23,77,"Haa nde Men udditunoo e ma…ì…ìe dammbugal immorde e Lepte sattu…óe …óen, e jaka kam…ìe e nder …óum ko …ìe ta∆¥ii…ìe e kala welo-welo e mo∆¥∆¥ere."
  23,78,"Alla O Senike ko Kanko woni On tagan∆äo on -ko onon yo fennu…ìe immital ngal- nan…óe …óen fii yo on nanir…óe, e gii…óe …óen fii yo on yi'ir…óe, e …ìer…óe …óen fii yo on faamir…óe, wonndude e …óum o yettatah Mo e dow …óii neemaaji si wonaa see…óa."
  23,79,"Ko Kanko woni On tagu∆äo on -onon yim…ìe …ìen- ka leydi, ko faade ka Makko Kanko tun √ëalnde Darngal moo…ìoyte …óon fii hasboore nden e njo…ìdi ndin."
  23,80,"Ko Kanko tun O Senike woni wurnoowo wurnoowo alah tanaa Makko, ko Kanko tun woni waroowo, waroowo alaa tanaa Makko, ko faade ka Makko Kanko tun hoddirtee luutondiral jemma on e √±alorma on, niwre e ndaygu juutugol e ra…ì…ìi…óugol. Enee on hakkiltaa kattan…óe Makko …óen, e bajjirgol Makko tagugol e fewjugol ngol?!"
  23,81,"Ko woni, …ìe wi'u yeru ko wi'unoo kon baabiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen e maamiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen ka keefeeru."
  23,82,"∆Åe wi'i e noone yeddugol wo…ó…óintina: "E jaka si men maayii men wontii mbullaari e ∆¥i'e ki…ó…óe e jaka menen ko men immintinoytee…ìe fii hasboore nden hara me…óen wuuri?!"."
  23,83,"Gom…óii men fodanooma ndee fodoore -…óum le ko immital …ìaawo mayde nden- maamiraa…ìe amen …ìen kadi fodano …óum ko adii, men yi'aali nden fodoore ka wa…ói, …óum wonaali si wonaa meere adinoo…ìe …ìen e penaale ma…ì…ìe."
  23,84,"Maakan -an Nulaa…óo- …ìee heefer…ìe yeddu…ìe immital ngal: "Ko hommbo jeyi ndii leydi, e …ìen wonu…ìe e hoore mayri si tawii hi…óon mari ganndal?""
  23,85,"Aray …ìe wi'i: "Leydi ndin e …ìen wonu…ìe e mayri ko Alla woodani". Awa maakan …ìe: "Enee, on annditatah wonndema On jey…óo leydi ndin e …ìen wonu…ìe e hoore mayri ko O Hattan∆äo e dow wurnitugol on …ìaawo mayde moo…óon?""
  23,86,"Maakan…ìe: "Ko hommbo woni Jooma kammuuli …óin jee…ói…ói? E ko hommbo woni Jooma Arsi mawki kin, kin tawki alaa ko tagaa ko …ìuriki mawnude?""
  23,87,"Aray …ìe wi'a: "Kammuuli …óin jee…ói…ói e Arsi mawki kin ko jeyal Alla." Maakan …ìe: "Enee, on hulirtah Alla doftagol yamiraa…ói Makko …óin e wo…ó…óitagol ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin fii yo on hisu immorde e Lepte Makko …óen?""
  23,88,"Maakan …ìe: "Ko e junngo hommbo woni laamu kala huunde, hay e huunde sortotaako e ley Laamu Makko ngun, hara Kanko hiMo faaboo on mo O muuyi immorde e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, alah hay e gooto ha…óanoowo on mo O muuyani bone, o dunyatah Lepte …óen e makko, si tawii laatanike on ganndal?""
  23,89,"Aray …ìe wi'a: "Laamu kala huunde ko e Junngo Makko woni O Senike. Awa maakan …ìe: "E ko honno hakkillaaji mo'on …óin yaari, hi…óon rewa tanaa Makko wonndude e qirritagol moo…óon …óum [ko ja≈ãtaa …óoo]"."